ENTRY            A1230   20260217   20260508   20260508       A133
SUBENT        A1230001   20260217   20260508   20260508       A133
BIB                  8         23
TITLE      Structure of 7Be. (II) The 6Li(p,p")6Li** and
           4He(3He,p")6Li** reactions
AUTHOR     (W.D.Harrison)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,92,260,1967)
           (T,HARRISON,1966) - Tables; technical details
REL-REF    (O,C1003001,W.D.Harrison+,J,PR,132,2607,1963) - Elastic
           scattering of protons by Li6 (same data in Table 1 of
           thesis)
           (O,A1397001,W.D.Harrison+,J,NP/A,92,253,1967) -
             (I) The 6Li(p,p')6Li* reaction
INSTITUTE  (1USACAL)
FACILITY   (VDGT,1USACAL)
METHOD     (PHD) In set of measurements the total cross section
           was determined by measuring at one angle the yield of
           the 3.56 MeV de-excitation gamma-rays to the 6Li
           ground state.
HISTORY    (19820511C) Compilation produced by Arzamas RFNC-VNIIEF
           (19990305U)CNPD: corrected 4-dig. year and lower cases.
           (20250831A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
           Subent 002 was split in two.
           (20260217A) SD: The digitized data were replaced with
           tabulated data from thesis. Corrections in all Subents.
           Subent 006 added.
ENDBIB              23
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           26
SUBENT        A1230002   20260217   20260508   20260508       A133
BIB                  6         16
REACTION   (3-LI-6(P,INL)3-LI-6,PAR,DA,,LEG)
COMMENT    At 5.80-MeV incident proton lab energy both the direct
           measurement and the coincidence data were used in
           calculations.
MISC-COL   (MISC) 7Be center-of-momentum energy.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-1) Standard errors
STATUS     (TABLE,,W.D.Harrison,T,HARRISON,1967) Table 6. Similar
           data presented on fig.1 of NP/A,92,260,1967
           (DEP,A1230003) Angular distributions.
           (DEP,A1230005) The coefficient of P0 (=the total c.m.
           cross section divided by 4Pi).
HISTORY    (20250831A) SD: SF9=EXP deleted from REACTION code.
           STATUS updated. EN-CM -> E-EXC-CMP; EN-ERR -> E-ERR-DIG
           Part of data moved to Subent 005. Data were redigitized
           (20260217A) SD: BIB updated. The digitized data were
           replaced with tabulated data from thesis.
ENDBIB              16
